{"tid":2347385,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MIRROR半百粉絲夾道歡迎  周柏豪現身攞獎被叫「收皮」","createTime":"2020-12-31T04:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T04:36:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5c4cc10beb0ba468aa5fa5bc449e863c0c1ea5","tid":2347385,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201231/GASSB54YOBERRNHGREZW2DONJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201231%2FGASSB54YOBERRNHGREZW2DONJM%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm5FIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=35d54a4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201231%2FGASSB54YOBERRNHGREZW2DONJM%2F&h=12d41760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201231/GASSB54YOBERRNHGREZW2DONJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nMIRROR半百粉絲夾道歡迎 <br />\n周柏豪現身攞獎被叫「收皮」<br />\n<br />\n新城電台昨日於葵涌一工業大廈的私人場地舉行《新城勁爆頒獎禮2020》，並在網上直播，組合MIRROR、周柏豪、鄭欣宜、江海迦（AGA）、關智斌及許廷鏗等多位歌手現身領獎（見附表）。周柏豪早前接受撐警陳百祥訪問，以「孝順阿媽」來比喻香港和內地，被大批網民狂轟。昨日是周柏豪表忠後首度現身，落車後傳媒叫他做訪問，但他卻越叫越走直接上樓，更被後輩MIRROR搶盡風頭。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：梁祖堯開條件任《造星IV》導師<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DXQhFe6yl7Mpct0G7c-xaCfZagE=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4DDTPZHGRRGQZAE7YKUHO5C7YM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDXQhFe6yl7Mpct0G7c-xaCfZagE%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4DDTPZHGRRGQZAE7YKUHO5C7YM.jpg&h=806dd1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■MIRROR昨日滿載而歸，組合獲得「勁爆組合」外，成員姜濤獲得「勁爆人氣偶像」，Anson Kong、Jer和Anson Lo就橫掃「勁爆新人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/llFVNt6ZQa9huclUrAQ-DtwKAtQ=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SFJ3PY2ZZVE45JCCGSTC3R4CBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FllFVNt6ZQa9huclUrAQ-DtwKAtQ%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSFJ3PY2ZZVE45JCCGSTC3R4CBI.jpg&h=f0f03f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■逾半百粉絲到場支持MIRROR，MIRROR座駕離開時，更排成兩排歡送。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Ssc-IEAs8wnWukKpici16BLhdc=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UYGDRURDXZG4LMQYOLBTJ5USIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Ssc-IEAs8wnWukKpici16BLhdc%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUYGDRURDXZG4LMQYOLBTJ5USIY.jpg&h=6e4ab1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在新城獲得兩個豬肉獎的周柏豪，已預告明日會缺席《叱咤》避風頭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5ARDSFxt2agya7LytFZ1QEcjY_Y=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZBUJXPQQL5ET3E5U3B52OTSVDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5ARDSFxt2agya7LytFZ1QEcjY_Y%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZBUJXPQQL5ET3E5U3B52OTSVDY.jpg&h=342435e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周柏豪人氣跌至冰點，昨日不獲粉絲到場支持，人丁單薄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提「阿媽論」即閃人<br />\n<br />\n周柏豪獲得「勁爆男歌手」時有感而發說：「做乜都好，最緊要係屋企人開心平安。」網民隨即在fb直播洗版鬧爆「收皮」，令新城要暫停留言功能，相反MIRROR則從頭到尾都獲洗版式支持。離開時被問到「孝順阿媽」論，周柏豪避談：「唔評論。」又指身為歌手出席頒獎禮是責任，隨即登車速逃。<br />\n<br />\n昨日大部份歌手包括周柏豪，皆要在大廈停車場外落車，但人氣爆燈的MIRROR的座駕可直駛入停車場才落車，當成員抵達時逾半百粉絲蜂擁而上，有貨車司機怒斥粉絲：「係咪唔要命，留返條命睇啦！」離開時粉絲更排成兩邊歡送MIRROR，相反其他歌星沒有粉絲到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zoKredgaSmkf2lLIWoCmRK3YVSg=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DVPPUV2TCRH5FDY6CXSSOSXBKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzoKredgaSmkf2lLIWoCmRK3YVSg%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDVPPUV2TCRH5FDY6CXSSOSXBKM.jpg&h=9ff85ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華納歌手衛蘭昨日出席最後的新城活動，她表示與新城DJ是好友，仍會約見面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jKkVGWHvlagDZAANLNUtRWny5UU=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3TKMY6DNWVE3TC2PLKIZGLEMIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjKkVGWHvlagDZAANLNUtRWny5UU%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3TKMY6DNWVE3TC2PLKIZGLEMIA.jpg&h=097cd036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■莫文蔚獲得「年度歌手」外，亦憑《呼吸有害》奪勁爆歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許廷鏗：個圈係圓<br />\n<br />\n頒獎禮上主持范振鋒、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nDear Jane昨日憑《銀河修理員》獲得「勁爆播放指數歌曲」，此曲日前殺入明晚舉行的商台《叱咤樂壇頒獎禮》的「我最喜愛的歌曲」最後五強，有網民指此曲是抗爭歌，會投票支持，主音阿Tim表示：「好開心首歌connect到大家。」另外，商台的《叱咤樂壇頒獎禮》將於明晚在九展舉行，除在商台網上播出外，ViuTV亦會同時直播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RUS1qR8_hU_BoEDIsxCJOkB7Hls=/709x952/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HYV4FPIEZNHZ5NZ45M5GPL2UKE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRUS1qR8_hU_BoEDIsxCJOkB7Hls%3D%2F709x952%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHYV4FPIEZNHZ5NZ45M5GPL2UKE.gif&h=7c30b626&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"344c3b2d3cae9e654f5f2c548d2f04f4228c93b5","tid":2347385,"uid":76804,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"周柏豪呢個撚樣第一個最必要狙擊<br />\n食候生市場可以奶到雪雪聲<br />\ngem都無佢咁可恥"},{"pid":"cf00663c4fe3a95cfe1484d7abb119dd67b20a13","tid":2347385,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"方皓玟呢？"},{"pid":"e2650866057f3d521c941530fb39b760ce5163ab","tid":2347385,"uid":112416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"天堂鳥？原來仲生存緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54914ecb7517a2139e58fe5ef45114eda4c89fbc","tid":2347385,"uid":244361,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"「其他歌手沒有粉絲到場...」<br />\n因為根本冇通知<br />\n點解鏡粉會知喺邊我真係好想知<br />\n有人特登放料搵人嚟造勢？<br />\n<br />\n琴日Fb又全程洗版<br />\n其他歌手拎獎唱歌都係咁mirror姜濤Ian<br />\n真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}